reviewText: I chose this rating because it is every show in its entirety, not edited out for time. It is also all the shows as opposed to just a select few shows from that season like the A&E show that was the bounty hunters previous show. I also chose this rating because I like the show! If you like Dog the Bounty Hunter, I would recommend this to you and anyone else that likes cop type shows.
I love this show very much. Dog and Beth are awesome bounty hunters. They try to make the world a better place one day at a time.
Excellent!
